{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/AboutRecoil /","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>참고: <a href=\"https://abangpa1ace.tistory.com/212\">https://abangpa1ace.tistory.com/212</a>, <a href=\"https://recoiljs.org/ko/docs/introduction/getting-started/\">https://recoiljs.org/ko/docs/introduction/getting-started/</a> , <a href=\"https://www.daleseo.com/react-suspense/\">https://www.daleseo.com/react-suspense/</a></p>\n<p>사이드 프로젝트를 하면서 검색한 뒤 지도에 띄워 줄 데이터를 대상으로 Redux와 Recoil을 많이 고민했지만 보일러 플레이트가 적고, 간편한 장점으로 Recoil을 택하였다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"recoil이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#recoil%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"recoil이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Recoil이란?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>- Recoil은 React 프로젝트를 위한 전역 상태관리 라이브러리 중 하나로 2020년 5월에 facebook에서 출시 했다. React 역시 같은 facebook에서 출시하여 다른 라이브러리와 달리 React 전용이며 React에 최적화 되어 있다고 말할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"다른-라이브러리도-많은데-왜-등장-했을까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EB%A5%B8-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%8F%84-%EB%A7%8E%EC%9D%80%EB%8D%B0-%EC%99%9C-%EB%93%B1%EC%9E%A5-%ED%96%88%EC%9D%84%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"다른 라이브러리도 많은데 왜 등장 했을까 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다른 라이브러리도 많은데 왜 등장 했을까?</h2>\n<p>가장 많이 쓰이는 Redux와 비교해보자</p>\n<ul>\n<li>- Redux는 React 전용 라이브러리가 아니다 따라서 React 관점에서는 외부 요인으로 store가 취급되며, 동시성 모드를 구현하기에 호환성이 부족하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<h6 id=\"동시성-모드concurrent\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8F%99%EC%8B%9C%EC%84%B1-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%9Cconcurrent\" aria-label=\"동시성 모드concurrent permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>동시성 모드(Concurrent)</h6>\n<p>Concurrent 모드는 React 앱이 응답성을 유지하고 사용자의 장치 기능과 네트워크 속도에 맞게 적절하게 조정하는 데 도움이 되는 일련의 새로운 기능이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>- 복잡한 보일러 플레이트를 가진 초기세팅이 요구된다. Store, Action, Reducer 등 다양한 구성요소가 필요하며 러닝커브가 높다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- 비동기 데이터에 추가 리소스가 요구된다. redux-saga 처럼 전역상태에 비동기 데이터를 호출하기 위한 서드 파티 라이브러리가 필요하다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"그럼-recoil은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8%EB%9F%BC-recoil%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"그럼 recoil은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그럼 Recoil은?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>- Recoil은 React 전용 라이브러리인 만큼 React 내부 접근성이 용이하다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- React 동시성 모드, Suspense 등을 지원하기 때문에 사용자 경험 관점에서도 매우 유리한 웹 어플리케이션을 만들 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- 전역상태의 설정/정의가 매우 간단하며 Recoil이 지원하는 Hooks로 get/set하기 때문에 React 문법과 매우 유사하다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- 보일러 플레이트가 눈에 띄게 줄어들며 사용방법도 간단해 러닝커브가 낮다는 장점이 있다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"recoil-세팅하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#recoil-%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"recoil 세팅하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Recoil 세팅하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>- 설치</li>\n</ul>\n<p>npm이나 yarn이나 명령어는 같으며 해당 포스팅은 npm으로 진행한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"shell\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">$npm install recoil</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>- 적용</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Recoil을 적용시키기 위해 최상단 app에 작성하였습니다.</p>\n<p>상태 관리는 따로 /src/state 디렉토리를 만들어 관리한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"tsx\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">//app.tsx</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">import</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> type { AppProps } </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">from</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;next/app&#39;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">import</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> { RecoilRoot } </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">from</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;recoil&#39;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">export</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">default</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">function</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">App</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">({ </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-11 grvsc-t4tStz-6\">Component</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">, </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-11 grvsc-t4tStz-6\">pageProps</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> }</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">:</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">AppProps</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">return</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">RecoilRoot</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">      &lt;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">Component</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> {</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">...</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">pageProps} /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">RecoilRoot</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  )</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"주요-개념-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"주요 개념 정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 개념 정리</h2>\n<h4 id=\"1-atoms\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-atoms\" aria-label=\"1 atoms permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Atoms</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>- Recoil 상태의 단위를 의미한다. 컴포넌트간에 이 상태는 공유되며, 구독 및 업데이트가 가능하다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- atom의 상태가 업데이트되면, 이를 구독하던 컴포넌트들이 모두 리렌더링 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- atom을 할당할 때 key, default값을 필수로 설정해야한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>- key: 사용할 데이터의 고유한 key 값</li>\n<li>- default: atom의 초기값</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ex)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"tsx\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">import</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> {atom} </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">from</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;recoil&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">export</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">searchList</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">atom</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">&lt;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">string</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">&gt;({</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  key: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;textState&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  default: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">});</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"2-전역-상태-관련-hooks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-hooks\" aria-label=\"2 전역 상태 관련 hooks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 전역 상태 관련 Hooks</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>- useRecoilState() : ustState()와 유사하며 [state, setState] 튜플에 할당하며, 인자에 Atoms또는 Selector를 넣어준다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- useRecoilValue() : 전역상태의 state 상태값만을 참조하기 위해 사용된다. 선언된 변수에 할당하여 사용하면 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- useSetRecoilState() : 전역상태의 setter 함수만을 활용하기 위해 사용된다. 선언된 함수변수에 할당하여 사용하면 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>- useResetRecoilState() : 전역상태를 default로 Reset 하기 위해 사용된다. 선언된 함수변수에 할당하여 사용하면 된다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ex)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"tsx\" 